data.description: Welcome to the beautiful end unit townhome with a huge backyard you’ve been waiting for! This meticulously cared for space has tons of important updates. In the past year, a new water heater, new sliding glass door, new retaining wall. In the last 2-3 years the seller installed a new A/C unit, carpet, bathroom updates and painted the garage. Since purchased, there has also been master bedroom and kitchen updates including a new dishwasher and garbage disposal. The layout gives room for dining with a spacious living room while still maintaining the desired open concept feel. You also won’t be disappointed to see all the bedrooms on one level. The home is minutes away from shopping, food, entertainment, North Mississippi Regional Park and easy highway access. This is the definition of a well taken care of home in a great location. You don’t want to miss this.
